videos.headline: Caitlin Clark hits the layup amid a shaky start
videos.description: Caitlin Clark drives in the paint for a layup but has missed eight of her first nine shots.

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark's OT 3 seals Big Ten title over Nebraska
videos.description: Caitlin Clark hits a deep 3-pointer in overtime to stave off Nebraska and win the Big Ten title for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark's OT 3 seals Big Ten title over Nebraska) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark scores her 2nd bucket of the game
videos.description: Caitlin Clark takes it in herself and sneaks in a layup against Nebraska late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark gives Iowa first lead of the game
videos.description: Caitlin Clark drives in for another layup to give Iowa their first lead of the game 53-52 against Nebraska.
